### 2. Topic Discovery via DomainParticipantListener

**Callback signature (Fast DDS 3.x):**
```cpp
void on_data_writer_discovery(
    DomainParticipant* participant,
    eprosima::fastdds::rtps::WriterDiscoveryStatus reason,
    const eprosima::fastdds::dds::PublicationBuiltinTopicData& info,
    bool& should_be_ignored) override
```

**Note on v3 migration:** In Fast DDS 2.x this was called `on_publisher_discovery()` with `WriterDiscoveryInfo&&`. The v3 API renamed it and changed the parameter types.

**WriterDiscoveryStatus enum values** (in `eprosima::fastdds::rtps`):
- `WriterDiscoveryStatus::DISCOVERED_WRITER`
- `WriterDiscoveryStatus::CHANGED_QOS_WRITER`
- `WriterDiscoveryStatus::REMOVED_WRITER`

**ReaderDiscoveryStatus** analogous enum values:
- `ReaderDiscoveryStatus::DISCOVERED_READER`
- `ReaderDiscoveryStatus::CHANGED_QOS_READER`
- `ReaderDiscoveryStatus::REMOVED_READER`

**PublicationBuiltinTopicData struct** (in `eprosima::fastdds::dds`, but migrated to `eprosima::fastdds::rtps` in v3):

```cpp
struct PublicationBuiltinTopicData {
    BuiltinTopicKey_t key;
    BuiltinTopicKey_t participant_key;
    fastcdr::string_255 topic_name;          // <-- topic name
    fastcdr::string_255 type_name;           // <-- type name
    TopicKind_t topic_kind;
    dds::xtypes::TypeInformationParameter type_information;  // <-- for TypeLookup
    // ... QoS fields (durability, reliability, etc.)
    GUID_t guid;
    RemoteLocatorList remote_locators;
    // ...
};
```

**Accessing fields:**
```cpp
info.topic_name   // fastcdr::string_255, implicitly converts to std::string
info.type_name    // fastcdr::string_255
info.type_information.type_information.complete().typeid_with_size().type_id()  // TypeIdentifier for TypeObject lookup
```

**Complete example from eProsima docs code tester:**
```cpp
void on_data_writer_discovery(
        DomainParticipant* participant,
        eprosima::fastdds::rtps::WriterDiscoveryStatus reason,
        const eprosima::fastdds::dds::PublicationBuiltinTopicData& info,
        bool& should_be_ignored) override
{
    should_be_ignored = false;
    switch (reason) {
        case eprosima::fastdds::rtps::WriterDiscoveryStatus::DISCOVERED_WRITER:
            std::cout << "New DataWriter on topic '" << info.topic_name
                      << "' of type '" << info.type_name << "'" << std::endl;
            break;
        case eprosima::fastdds::rtps::WriterDiscoveryStatus::CHANGED_QOS_WRITER:
            break;
        case eprosima::fastdds::rtps::WriterDiscoveryStatus::REMOVED_WRITER:
            std::cout << "DataWriter on topic '" << info.topic_name << "' left." << std::endl;
            break;
    }
}
```

Sources: [DomainParticipantListener (3.4)](https://fast-dds.docs.eprosima.com/en/latest/fastdds/dds_layer/domain/domainParticipantListener/domainParticipantListener.html), [Discovery Callbacks (3.4)](https://fast-dds.docs.eprosima.com/en/latest/fastdds/discovery/disc_callbacks.html), [PublicationBuiltinTopicData API (3.0.2)](https://fast-dds.docs.eprosima.com/en/v3.0.2/fastdds/api_reference/rtps/builtin/data/PublicationBuiltinTopicData.html), [Migration Guide (3.4)](https://fast-dds.docs.eprosima.com/en/3.4.x/notes/migration_guide.html)

